The average cumulative GPA threshold of 3.0 is commonly used in academic institutions as a benchmark for students' satisfactory performance.
; 
International students are those with 'is_international' set to 1, indicating their non-domestic student status.
; 
The current academic year and semester are determined by the 'is_current' flag set to 1 in the academic_years and semesters tables, signifying the present academic period.
